  "description": "<p><strong>今年晚些时候Xbox One就将上市，微软当前还不能喜新厌旧，在未来几年里Xbox 360不会被抛弃。为了继续博取Xbox 360用户的换新，微软下周将在Xbox Live市场中举办“终极游戏销售”活动，调低32款游戏的价格。</strong>微软Xbox Live主管Larry Hryb公布了这份游戏名单，其中不乏大作，例如刚刚发布的《生化奇兵》和《战争机器：审判》。不过Hryb表示自己现在也不知道这些游戏会以什么价格什么时候进行优惠销售，最近几日会有更多消息。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2df78aca/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242894.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%EF%BC%9A32%E6%AC%BEXbox+360%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E9%99%8D%E4%BB%B7%E4%BF%83%E9%94%80\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242894.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%EF%BC%9A32%E6%AC%BEXbox+360%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E9%99%8D%E4%BB%B7%E4%BF%83%E9%94%80\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242894.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%EF%BC%9A32%E6%AC%BEXbox+360%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E9%99%8D%E4%BB%B7%E4%BF%83%E9%94%80\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242894.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%EF%BC%9A32%E6%AC%BEXbox+360%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E9%99%8D%E4%BB%B7%E4%BF%83%E9%94%80\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242894.htm&amp;t=%E5%