  "description": "<p><strong>亚马逊悄然铺开进军高端艺术品市场的计划，该公司拟最早7月份在其网站开设一个全新板块，独家销售绘画、摄影作品及其他美术品。</strong>据知悉亚马逊此项计划的画廊经营者表示，亚马逊将率先在其网站上推出来自全美约100家小型画廊的艺术品。近几周来，亚马逊已陆续在其总部所在地西雅图、旧金山、纽约及其它城市举行了鸡尾酒会，邀请画廊参加这一新项目。亚马逊发言人未就此置评。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2df78ac7/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242893.htm&amp;t=%E4%BA%9A%E9%A9%AC%E9%80%8A%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E9%AB%98%E7%AB%AF%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA+%E6%8B%9F%E5%94%AE%E9%AB%98%E6%A1%A3%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%93%81\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242893.htm&amp;t=%E4%BA%9A%E9%A9%AC%E9%80%8A%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E9%AB%98%E7%AB%AF%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA+%E6%8B%9F%E5%94%AE%E9%AB%98%E6%A1%A3%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%93%81\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242893.htm&amp;t=%E4%BA%9A%E9%A9%AC%E9%80%8A%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E9%AB%98%E7%AB%AF%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA+%E6%8B%9F%E5%94%AE%E9%AB%98%E6%A1%A3%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%93%81\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242893.htm&amp;t=%E4%BA%9A%E9%A9%AC%E9%80%8A%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E9%AB%98%E7%AB%AF%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA+%E6%8B%9F%E5%94%AE%E9%AB%98%E6%A1%A3%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E5%93%81\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242893.htm&amp;t=%E4%BA%9A%E9%A9%AC